{"tid":2268721,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"<再賣> 美國將對台灣出售4架MQ-9無人機 裝置偵察設備","createTime":"2020-11-03T04:27:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-03T05:06:23.000Z","uid":227801,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"453bea08e6afb042aa00ceb2db0eef0f50c7f3bd","tid":2268721,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T04:27:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202011030005.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Ffirstnews%2F202011030005.aspx&d=tGWxp70K68wBh01xS7f0EkYZmLIq74JPLN0FyuDKESI%3D&h=35eb3edc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202011030005.aspx</a><br />\n（中央社華盛頓2日綜合外電報導）路透社今天引述消息人士報導，美國出售台灣4架MQ-9無人機案，已在國會進入最後批准階段，軍售金額為6億美元（約171億台幣）。<br />\n<br />\n消息人士之一透露，美國國務院可能會在本週稍後正式知會國會，然後國會有30天時間可提出反對；不過因美國兩大黨目前都支持台灣防務，所以國會不致於反對。<br />\n這4架MQ-9海上衛士（Sea Guardian）型無人機是由通用原子航空系統公司（General Atomics Aeronautical Systems Inc.）建造，將與相關地面站台和代訓一併出售。<br />\n消息人士說，儘管此型無人機可裝配武器，不過對台出售的4架MQ-9將裝置偵察設備。（譯者：張佑之）1091103<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=411424\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D411424&d=tGWxp70K68wBh01xS7f0EkYZmLIq74JPLN0FyuDKESI%3D&h=52388c05\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D411424&h=216d9c26\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=411424</a><br />\n【Now新聞台】路透社報道，美國向台灣出售MQ-9無人機的計劃，已進入國會審批關鍵程序。<br />\n<br />\n路透社引述消息人士指，美國將會向台灣出售四架總值六億美元的MQ-9海上衛士無人機，軍售案已進入關鍵階段，正等待國會作最後審批。如果軍售案獲落實，將會是特朗普政府放寬出口無人機技術限制後，首次對外出售先進的無人機。<br />\n<br />\n除了無人機，美國還會向台灣提供地面站設施及訓練。"},{"pid":"6aef6462aac040f64c606a6f07f539f719ba990a","tid":2268721,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T04:30:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1d5353b61591638207b3d2b02ab0e56599a286d","tid":2268721,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T04:45:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bafbf975249108f9cea3cbd7e5311a7a2a90b95","tid":2268721,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T05:00:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"951d98ca87e6ae56244fa357d6fd0902ca4d7792","tid":2268721,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T05:06:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}